{
  "stem": "10587.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they also put wood on top of it, you know, and so that the Germans couldn't-- and so when we came there, was no room for us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was like a-- real like a grave, that they slept in, enough room for, you know, sideways to lie, for four people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we couldn't get down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were hiding in the same storage bin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a lot of wood, firewood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were there maybe a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the German, the-- I don't know whether it was the Wehrmacht or the SS group, which at that time it was totally confusing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they said, we know you are there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're going count to three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you don't come out, we will throw in a grenade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father immediately said, come on, boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went out and raised his arms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and so then they took us to a collecting place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know what exactly happened at the same time to my cousin Jack and, and his, his father, mother, and the, and the-- his younger brother.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But maybe they just remained there for a while, maybe same day, maybe the next day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- because they were satisfied that we came out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we, we were taken to this collecting place, where they put us on a cattle train [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and took us Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a, it was a train that had a roof with-- but it had little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] openings, you know, for the cattle to be able to breathe.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, they-- when they open the-- I mean, when they lock the door, you get such a click, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- I felt like the click in my heart, because I knew where we are going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was very chaotic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were kids, babies, on the floor, my father, myself in the train-- mothers, pregnant women, [CRYING] old people, young people, people my age, people my brother's age.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how long we were on the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I remember that the kids were crying, and there was such a chaos, so-- so I collected whatever I could-- sugar, candy or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I, I sit down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I played with the kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because I knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[CRYING] [INAUDIBLE] And-- and it got-- and it became worse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Germans came, the SS troopers, when we arrived in Auschwitz, took these babies and threw them against the train and threw them down on the ground, stepped on their heads with their boots.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was such a chaos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were running around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The SS group was hitting people with the butts of their rifle, rifle butts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Dogs were barking and biting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] seemed like you just arrived in hell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was a picture that I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Mothers crying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took the babies away from them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They threw them on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They stepped on their heads, threw them against the car.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Old people, they kicked and beat and, and hit them constantly with rifle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Blood was all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] then they was an officer there who was-- to me, it looked like a little baton, in the faces, right and left, right and left.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, I was holding onto my brother in one hand and my father on the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, and he says-- the SS trooper said, he cannot go with you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they tried to separate us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then I said to my brother, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'll, I'll come across.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In Polish I told him, and I'll get you back here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was the last I saw of-- this was the last that I saw my brother, Joshua.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they marched us in through a gate where it says, 'Arbeit Macht Frei'.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This was engraved on my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And, and I can still see it in front of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And, and we went through, took us on another barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And, and we had to strip completely, and took everything away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were standing nude.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and they deloused us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had those pumps with powder, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what they call [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] delousing, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they will getted all the lice, kill them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, we were standing in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
